      "created_at": "2017-06-23T15:03:42.076Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Kjo nuk eshte foto e dites ngaqe nuk lejohen fotot.</p>\n<aside class=\"onebox whitelistedgeneric\">\n  <header class=\"source\">\n      <img src=\"https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/community_logos/52517/voxv.png\" class=\"site-icon\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.vox.com/policy-and-politics/2017/6/22/15855124/jim-acosta-twitter-cnn-press-briefing-spicer\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"02:20PM - 22 June 2017\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Vox – 22 Jun 17</a>\n  </header>\n  <article class=\"onebox-body\">\n    <div class=\"aspect-image\" style=\"--aspect-ratio:626/328;\"><img src=\"https://cdn0.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/ubk-rsgRzgMxmGefqpg-1EMqOjw=/0x0:626x328/fit-in/1200x630/cdn1.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/8733399/Screen_Shot_2017_06_22_at_1.09.56_PM.png\" class=\"thumbnail\"></div>\n\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.vox.com/policy-and-politics/2017/6/22/15855124/jim-acosta-twitter-cnn-press-briefing-spicer\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">A CNN reporter lost it at the Trump White House on Twitter</a></h3>\n\n<p>Jim Acosta is livid about off camera press briefings.</p>\n\n\n  </article>\n  <div class=\"onebox-metadata\">\n    \n    \n  </div>\n  <div style=\"clear: both\"></div>\n</aside>\n\n<p>P.S. kerkoj falje qe dola jashte teme. Blendi mund ta fshije komentin tim.</p>",
